summary: Some new model resources for Halloween 2014
descriptionHtml:
This years Witches Festival is soon upon us !

 Some new model resources for Halloween 2014

 There is an area in game to see the models...at the Witches Festival...near Half Moon Mill

 Included in this package :
  --three glass skulls-  green, red, orange
  --two festival ropes - skulls and pumpkins
  --three crystal balls- clear, clear with sparks inside, and swirling blue mist inside
  --a monster tree holding evil and happy pumpkins
  --a blood alembic
  --a set of dungeon keys
  --a pile of bones
  --three bats-one mounted, one loose, one in a cage
  --two mounted skull and crossbones-bloody and white
  --a flying skull with bat wings
  --two offerings bowls-one empty, one with sigil stone
  --a witchboard with planchet
  --a tent re-textured
  --a door with skull handle, or just the handle
  --a building
  --the witches festival sign on a pole, or loose
  --my pet spider in a tank
  --witches throne
  --witches throne stand

Please do not upload any place else..Thanks and happy modding !
author: badgremlin
